<L>__{exterior house – the duel}
<A>__{derek throws open the door and before the black man standing guard can wheel, derek, tounge pressed violently against his teeth, buries three bullets in his chest. the force propels the man six feet backwards.}
<L>__{interior jetta trunk – the bag of coke}
<A>__{the other man, stunned by the exchange of gunfire, quickly grabs the stuff and charges back to the awaiting trans am. in tight skivvies, and without hesitation, derek buries a bullet in the other man’s shoulder. the man falls to the ground, the bag of cocaine dropping safely to the grass. from the getaway car, the driver fires off a late volley of bullets but they miss derek wide. derek faces the car, walks towards it, and fearlessly fires shot after shot at the driver as the car speeds down the street.}
